9
00:00:21.414 --> 00:00:22.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, I suppose it is.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:22.813 --> 00:00:24.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are we to dismantle this piece of art?</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:25.083 --> 00:00:25.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:26.692 --> 00:00:28.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if we don't, Keiko'll dismantle me.</c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:46.846 --> 00:00:48.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy.</c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:48.645 --> 00:00:49.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi, sweetie.</c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:50.165 --> 00:00:51.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:54.884 --> 00:00:55.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi.</c.bg_transparent>

17
