<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, Daddy! I have a little brother</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:01:12.497 --> 00:01:14.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? Is that him?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:01:15.936 --> 00:01:17.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He's in there.</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:01:19.415 --> 00:01:20.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:22.974 --> 00:01:23.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A baby?</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:25.514 --> 00:01:29.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah. I--I thought you'd be happy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, we talked about it</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:29.956 --> 00:01:31.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and decided we'd start trying.</c.bg_transparent>

26
