<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We--We--Well, but your last visit,</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:35.951 --> 00:01:37.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you were only here the one night, and...</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:38.350 --> 00:01:40.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought it'd take a couple of nights.</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:40.830 --> 00:01:44.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest... a lot more nights.</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:44.997 --> 00:01:46.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess we just got lucky this time.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:49.276 --> 00:01:50.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess so.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:01:58.588 --> 00:01:59.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
