<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure this is a good time?</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:02:21.418 --> 00:02:22.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he'll be able to fit you in.</c.bg_transparent>

40
