<c.bg_transparent>Thank you so much for doing this, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:02:24.936 --> 00:02:25.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'm glad to.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:02:29.016 --> 00:02:30.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They can take the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Rubicon.</i></c.bg_transparent>

43
00:02:30.495 --> 00:02:31.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:02:31.774 --> 00:02:32.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
