47
00:02:37.112 --> 00:02:38.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're hoping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get the Emissary's blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:02:40.595 --> 00:02:40.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring them in.</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:02:44.110 --> 00:02:46.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You remember the words?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The marriage blessing?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:02:46.030 --> 00:02:47.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think so.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:02:50.228 --> 00:02:53.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary, we're very grateful to you</c.bg_transparent>
