52
00:02:53.667 --> 00:02:54.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:02:55.248 --> 00:02:56.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, if you'll just join hands...</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:03:00.246 --> 00:03:03.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Zhia'kala, tar'eh anu suur...</i></c.bg_transparent>

55
00:03:04.165 --> 00:03:06.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>te'von, aka'lu rez... ka'vor</i></c.bg_transparent>

56
00:03:07.124 --> 00:03:08.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>mat'ana kel.</i></c.bg_transparent>

57
00:03:09.563 --> 00:03:10.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:03:10.083 --> 00:03:11.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you very much.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:03:16.421 --> 00:03:18.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your accent is getting</c.bg_transparent>
