60
00:03:19.380 --> 00:03:20.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:03:23.819 --> 00:03:25.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighing )</c.bg_transparent>

62
