131
00:09:28.762 --> 00:09:29.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Major Kira"?</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:09:30.582 --> 00:09:31.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:31.122 --> 00:09:33.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But your family would be part</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the artist</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> D'jarra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra?</i></c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:37.126 --> 00:09:38.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor used to have a strict caste system.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:39.265 --> 00:09:42.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A person's work was dictated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by what family they were born into.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:44.464 --> 00:09:46.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You no longer follow your </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras?</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:46.863 --> 00:09:48.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Cardassians occupied Bajor,</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:48.623 --> 00:09:51.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we gave up the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so that we could fight them.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:52.521 --> 00:09:53.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all became soldiers.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Cardassians occupied Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:57.360 --> 00:09:58.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For over 50 years.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:01.919 --> 00:10:03.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems you're right, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:03.678 --> 00:10:06.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A great deal has happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since I've been gone.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:14.515 --> 00:10:16.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you look at the prophecies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Emissary,</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:16.954 --> 00:10:20.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>a lot of them make much more sense</c.bg_transparent>
