00:10:20.493 --> 00:10:20.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:21.513 --> 00:10:24.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every text I've read says</c.bg_transparent>
