00:10:27.290 --> 00:10:28.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he would find the Celestial Temple</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:28.931 --> 00:10:31.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that there, the Prophets would give</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>him back his life.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:32.210 --> 00:10:33.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:33.669 --> 00:10:35.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't give me back my life.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:36.828 --> 00:10:39.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not literally, but they did help you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>get your life back together.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:39.567 --> 00:10:41.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>True enough, but I wasn't the first one</c.bg_transparent>

