<c.bg_transparent>to find the wormhole,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or to meet the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:45.207 --> 00:10:46.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
