00:10:50.784 --> 00:10:51.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:52.363 --> 00:10:55.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why are you using them</c.bg_transparent>
