00:10:56.242 --> 00:10:58.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I was looking for something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to convince me</c.bg_transparent>

