172
00:11:27.994 --> 00:11:29.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you're off the hook.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:29.673 --> 00:11:30.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How does it feel?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:31.792 --> 00:11:33.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It feels, uh... good.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:34.711 --> 00:11:36.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more ceremonies to attend.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:11:36.710 --> 00:11:38.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more blessings to give.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:11:39.049 --> 00:11:42.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more prophecies to fulfill.</c.bg_transparent>
