<c.bg_transparent>the Dominion and the Maquis.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:49.967 --> 00:11:51.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel like I'm on vacation.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:59.523 --> 00:12:00.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief!</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:01.483 --> 00:12:02.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Dad.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:03.042 --> 00:12:04.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You heard?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Great news, my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:05.042 --> 00:12:07.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Come have a drink. Celebrate.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I really should be getting home.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:09.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, just one.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:09.868 --> 00:12:10.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

187
