<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien is having a baby.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:16.598 --> 00:12:18.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought your females carried your young.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:19.317 --> 00:12:22.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My wife. My wife is having the baby.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:23.237 --> 00:12:24.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:25.036 --> 00:12:27.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when my nephew Nog was a baby.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:28.035 --> 00:12:30.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cutest thing you ever saw.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:31.233 --> 00:12:32.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know babies.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:12:32.457 --> 00:12:34.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every little thing they pick up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>goes straight into their ears.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:35.452 --> 00:12:37.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I used to love reading to him.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:38.211 --> 00:12:43.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, "See Brak acquire.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Acquire, Brak, acquire."</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:45.969 --> 00:12:48.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just think. Soon there'll be two</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>little O'Briens</c.bg_transparent>

