00:12:48.611 --> 00:12:49.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>scampering about underfoot.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:51.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hard to believe, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:52.208 --> 00:12:54.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mind you, they do say the second</c.bg_transparent>
