202
00:12:54.189 --> 00:12:56.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>since you've already been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through all the diapers</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:56.260 --> 00:12:58.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the endless crying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the sleepless nights.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:59.859 --> 00:13:01.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Cheers.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:01.779 --> 00:13:03.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh... cheers.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:04.737 --> 00:13:05.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:06.857 --> 00:13:09.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. Nothing at all. I couldn't be happier.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:09.296 --> 00:13:11.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: Did you hear?</c.bg_transparent>
