00:26:45.117 --> 00:26:46.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can Daddy color, too?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:46.318 --> 00:26:47.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm coloring.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:27:13.109 --> 00:27:16.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The four-shift rotation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>also seems to be improving performance.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:27:16.388 --> 00:27:17.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Less mistakes due to fatigue.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:18.668 --> 00:27:21.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine. Let's make the change permanent.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Anything else?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:27:24.446 --> 00:27:26.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was wondering if, in the next few days</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:27:26.567 --> 00:27:29.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you would have the time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to meet with Major Jatarn.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:27:30.510 --> 00:27:30.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sure.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:27:33.485 --> 00:27:34.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:36.125 --> 00:27:37.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:38.442 --> 00:27:40.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just received a communiqué</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Starfleet Command</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:40.964 --> 00:27:43.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>responding to my report</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Bajoran situation.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:44.080 --> 00:27:44.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That bad?</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:45.380 --> 00:27:45.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not yet,</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:46.839 --> 00:27:48.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I can read between the lines.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:51.457 --> 00:27:54.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was sent here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help bring Bajor into the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:55.796 --> 00:27:58.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't look like much</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a possibility anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:27:58.296 --> 00:27:59.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As far as Starfleet is concerned,</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:28:00.435 --> 00:28:01.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have failed my mission.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:28:02.374 --> 00:28:05.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not fair. It's not your fault.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:28:06.214 --> 00:28:07.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is from where they're sitting.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:28:08.973 --> 00:28:12.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The irony is, Starfleet was always trying</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:28:12.415 --> 00:28:15.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to get me to distance myself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this Emissary business.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:28:15.231 --> 00:28:16.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And now that I have...</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:28:21.309 --> 00:28:23.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I could talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to First Minister Shakaar</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:23.428 --> 00:28:25.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>about sending Starfleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a communiqué explai--</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:25.548 --> 00:28:27.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It--it'll blow over.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:28.946 --> 00:28:30.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not that.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:28:31.986 --> 00:28:33.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I'm just feeling...</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:28:35.275 --> 00:28:35.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did fail.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:28:37.064 --> 00:28:37.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir...</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:28:38.864 --> 00:28:43.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anyway, why did you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>want me to meet Jatarn?</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:28:44.382 --> 00:28:45.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:28:46.761 --> 00:28:48.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can talk about that another time.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:28:48.641 --> 00:28:49.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it, Major?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:28:51.780 --> 00:28:53.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he'd make an excellent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>First Officer.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:28:55.818 --> 00:28:57.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As soon as you can find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to take my post,</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:28:57.979 --> 00:28:59.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to resign my commission.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:00.738 --> 00:29:01.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:01.618 --> 00:29:04.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To follow your...</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> D'jarra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

457
00:29:05.596 --> 00:29:07.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm planning to move back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Dahkur Province.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:29:07.637 --> 00:29:09.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are a lot of artists</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who live in the capital,</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:29:09.517 --> 00:29:11.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I have a friend there who's willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to apprentice me.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:13.487 --> 00:29:14.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:17.272 --> 00:29:20.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last thing I want to do is to add</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your problems.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:23.630 --> 00:29:25.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is something I have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:29.429 --> 00:29:31.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sniffles )</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:29:32.907 --> 00:29:34.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If, um...</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:29:35.646 --> 00:29:37.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't hit it off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Major Jatarn, um,</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:37.986 --> 00:29:39.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can think of a few other people.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:39.886 --> 00:29:41.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It shouldn't be that hard to find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to replace me.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:29:42.984 --> 00:29:46.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't doubt that I can find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone to fill your post...</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:29:49.493 --> 00:29:50.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But to replace you?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:29:58.051 --> 00:30:00.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens, closes )</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:06.717 --> 00:30:07.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, time.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:08.316 --> 00:30:10.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>1921 hours.</i></c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:10.716 --> 00:30:12.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's Dr. Bashir?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:12.155 --> 00:30:14.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dr. Bashir is in Quark's bar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:20.912 --> 00:30:23.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm chasing a triple 17</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a bull, Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:23.112 --> 00:30:23.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Got some catching up to do.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:24.591 --> 00:30:25.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief!</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:30:28.191 --> 00:30:29.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:30:33.789 --> 00:30:34.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:30:34.750 --> 00:30:35.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How have you been?</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:30:36.428 --> 00:30:37.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not bad. You?</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:30:37.418 --> 00:30:39.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you know, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:30:39.987 --> 00:30:42.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was heading home.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Thought I'd stop in for a quick pint.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:30:46.626 --> 00:30:47.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:30:47.785 --> 00:30:48.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been a while, eh?</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:30:48.896 --> 00:30:50.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ha. Seems like weeks.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:30:52.023 --> 00:30:53.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see you found someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to play darts with.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:30:53.861 --> 00:30:54.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:30:54.822 --> 00:30:56.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've set a board up in our quarters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so Molly and I can play.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:30:57.701 --> 00:30:59.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, Morn's, um... he's pretty good.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:30:59.541 --> 00:31:00.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So's Molly.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:01.780 --> 00:31:03.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not the same.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not the same.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:07.638 --> 00:31:11.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, Molly's just a kid.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, we've been playing with magnets.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:12.238 --> 00:31:15.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn couldn't hit a Yridian yak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at five paces.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:31:16.896 --> 00:31:17.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were evenly matched.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:31:18.415 --> 00:31:19.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had a good rivalry going on.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:31:19.655 --> 00:31:20.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, kept us sharp.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:31:20.935 --> 00:31:21.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:31:23.174 --> 00:31:23.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're late.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:31:25.933 --> 00:31:26.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:31:27.653 --> 00:31:30.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Thursday, and I've got your usual</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>holosuite reserved.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:31:30.413 --> 00:31:31.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't you cancel?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:31:31.712 --> 00:31:33.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I was, um, hoping maybe...</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:31:34.891 --> 00:31:36.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no, I--I--I got to get home.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:31:38.050 --> 00:31:41.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about you, Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Battle of Britain awaits.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:31:41.113 --> 00:31:43.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you know my policy on cancellations,</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:31:44.188 --> 00:31:45.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no refunds.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:31:45.787 --> 00:31:46.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:31:47.107 --> 00:31:51.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe Morn's better in the cockpit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a spitfire than he is at darts.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:31:50.826 --> 00:31:52.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, it wouldn't be the same.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:31:52.706 --> 00:31:55.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um... You're right.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:31:56.265 --> 00:31:58.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn probably doesn't even know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where England is.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:31:59.743 --> 00:32:00.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:32:02.983 --> 00:32:03.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see you.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:32:14.179 --> 00:32:15.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

516
00:32:15.938 --> 00:32:16.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:32:17.058 --> 00:32:19.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You'd better come down to the Promenade.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Someone's been killed.</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:32:23.676 --> 00:32:25.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What happened?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-We don't know yet.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:32:25.336 --> 00:32:28.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He fell from the second level.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>His neck was broken on impact.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:32:28.254 --> 00:32:30.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did anyone see it happen?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I did.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:32:32.580 --> 00:32:33.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Was it an accident?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:32:34.736 --> 00:32:35.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I pushed him.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:32:36.972 --> 00:32:40.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His family name is Imutta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Their </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>is unclean.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:32:42.192 --> 00:32:43.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They prepare the dead for burial.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:32:44.510 --> 00:32:47.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked him to set the proper example</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and resign from our order.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:32:48.628 --> 00:32:49.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He refused.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:32:49.868 --> 00:32:51.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You killed him because of his </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra?</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:32:52.687 --> 00:32:56.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to. If a Vedek can't do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what the Emissary has asked of us,</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:32:57.446 --> 00:32:58.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>how can we expect anyone else to?</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:00.045 --> 00:33:01.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get him out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:11.798 --> 00:33:13.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I regret what happened here today</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:13.581 --> 00:33:17.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as much as you do,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but change is never easy.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:18.219 --> 00:33:19.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The road that the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have asked us to walk</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:19.844 --> 00:33:21.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>won't always be a smooth one.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:21.919 --> 00:33:23.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And forcing people to follow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:24.178 --> 00:33:25.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>won't make it any smoother.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:25.857 --> 00:33:27.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened on the Promenade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was just the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:28.657 --> 00:33:29.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Must I remind you, Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:30.696 --> 00:33:32.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm merely fulfilling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the will of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:33.375 --> 00:33:34.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know that?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:33:36.294 --> 00:33:37.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:33:38.334 --> 00:33:39.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what you've done with the position</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:33:40.013 --> 00:33:41.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has made me wish I had never given it up.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:33:42.753 --> 00:33:45.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you did,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it was the right decision.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:33:46.012 --> 00:33:48.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never truly accepted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the role in the first place.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:33:51.509 --> 00:33:52.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm willing to accept it now.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:33:56.828 --> 00:33:58.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're challenging my claim.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:33:58.908 --> 00:34:00.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've left me no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:02.846 --> 00:34:03.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we went to the people</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:04.846 --> 00:34:08.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and asked them to choose</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between us, it would be chaos.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:08.154 --> 00:34:10.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to divide Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any more than you do.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:10.944 --> 00:34:12.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wouldn't be divided for long</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:12.523 --> 00:34:14.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because in the end,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the people would choose me.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:15.103 --> 00:34:17.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My claim was foretold</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the ancient texts.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:19.123 --> 00:34:22.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to find the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to be with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:24.180 --> 00:34:25.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me back my life.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:25.940 --> 00:34:29.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not going to settle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this by arguing over ancient texts.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:29.818 --> 00:34:30.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then how?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:30.979 --> 00:34:34.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's only one way to be sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which one of us is the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:34:35.676 --> 00:34:38.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to go to the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and ask the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:34:59.269 --> 00:35:00.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Going to half thrusters.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:35:02.308 --> 00:35:04.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:07.195 --> 00:35:07.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now what?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:09.095 --> 00:35:09.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We wait.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:34.539 --> 00:35:37.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( thudding heartbeat )</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:37.618 --> 00:35:39.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:39.777 --> 00:35:41.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the one that was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:42.176 --> 00:35:45.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I was. And you gave me back my life,</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:45.656 --> 00:35:47.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>just as the texts foretold.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:47.696 --> 00:35:49.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you here?</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:49.615 --> 00:35:53.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To... prove to this nonbeliever</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:53.394 --> 00:35:56.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you sent me to put Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back on the right path.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:35:57.951 --> 00:36:01.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, tell him you chose me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:36:02.351 --> 00:36:05.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell that him that I fulfilled</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the ancient prophecies,</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:36:06.109 --> 00:36:08.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that I was the first to find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Celestial Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:36:08.869 --> 00:36:12.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to meet with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He came to you centuries later.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:36:13.387 --> 00:36:14.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First...</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:36:15.666 --> 00:36:16.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Later...</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:36:17.625 --> 00:36:19.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have no meaning to us.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:36:20.246 --> 00:36:22.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The Bajorans believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you are their Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:36:22.604 --> 00:36:24.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That you have chosen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one of us to be your Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:36:31.063 --> 00:36:33.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We... are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:34.702 --> 00:36:35.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:40.860 --> 00:36:42.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are linear.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:42.839 --> 00:36:43.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It limits them.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:36:46.919 --> 00:36:48.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They do not understand.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:36:48.440 --> 00:36:49.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we want to understand.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:36:49.317 --> 00:36:50.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why we're here.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:36:51.526 --> 00:36:52.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You saved his life. Why?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:53.636 --> 00:36:54.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:36:55.615 --> 00:36:56.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We kept him with us.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:36:57.015 --> 00:36:59.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So that I would be spared the occupation.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:36:59.254 --> 00:37:01.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So that I could bring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>back to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:37:01.973 --> 00:37:03.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true?</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:37:03.584 --> 00:37:04.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that what you want?</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:37:07.033 --> 00:37:10.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>are part of what the Sisko</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would call the past.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:37:11.330 --> 00:37:14.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko taught us that for you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what was can never be again.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:37:15.888 --> 00:37:19.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> belong in the past,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why did you send me into the future?</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:37:24.385 --> 00:37:24.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:37:26.365 --> 00:37:28.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:37:28.845 --> 00:37:30.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying that he's your Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:37:32.444 --> 00:37:34.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:37:36.772 --> 00:37:38.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I've been wrong...</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:37:38.679 --> 00:37:39.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About everything.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:37:41.922 --> 00:37:42.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should have let me die.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:37:44.641 --> 00:37:46.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We still can.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:37:47.520 --> 00:37:48.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can return him</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:37:48.819 --> 00:37:50.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to the moment we found him.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:37:52.178 --> 00:37:53.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allow him to die.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:37:53.857 --> 00:37:54.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:55.716 --> 00:37:57.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why not return him to his own time</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:37:58.398 --> 00:38:03.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as he is now, uninjured,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so that he can get back safely to Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:38:08.833 --> 00:38:11.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He would remember</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>nothing of what has happened.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:38:13.611 --> 00:38:16.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could be with my wife and family.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:38:21.331 --> 00:38:22.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm ready to go home.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:38:24.650 --> 00:38:25.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:38:27.010 --> 00:38:28.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you stay here?</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:38:28.609 --> 00:38:30.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I still have questions.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:38:32.328 --> 00:38:34.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:38:34.996 --> 00:38:36.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What does that mean?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:38:37.515 --> 00:38:40.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You... </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:39:08.265 --> 00:39:10.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, Molly really loves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that book Jake gave her.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:39:10.655 --> 00:39:13.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She made me read it to her three times</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before she fell asleep.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:39:18.452 --> 00:39:19.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:39:20.052 --> 00:39:21.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to be working another few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:39:22.193 --> 00:39:25.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Well, that's okay.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll, uh... I'll read.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:39:26.450 --> 00:39:27.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you want to go do something...</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:39:28.210 --> 00:39:30.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:39:35.368 --> 00:39:36.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:39:37.486 --> 00:39:43.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, I promised I wouldn't say anything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's about Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:39:44.645 --> 00:39:45.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about him?</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:39:47.063 --> 00:39:49.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I ran into him the other day,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and he seemed depressed.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:39:49.443 --> 00:39:51.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'd never admit it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he really misses you.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:39:52.522 --> 00:39:53.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor guy.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:39:54.621 --> 00:39:56.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No family to come home to every night.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:39:57.540 --> 00:40:00.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you should go find him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, cheer him up a little.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:40:01.739 --> 00:40:03.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Depressed, is he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Very.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:40:03.819 --> 00:40:05.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I should go spend an hour with him.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:40:05.619 --> 00:40:06.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe two.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:40:12.976 --> 00:40:14.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a lucky man.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:40:19.095 --> 00:40:20.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keiko to Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:40:20.894 --> 00:40:21.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

643
00:40:22.532 --> 00:40:23.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian, it's about Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:40:24.212 --> 00:40:28.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I promised I wouldn't tell anyone,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>but he's been really depressed lately.</i></c.bg_transparent>

645
00:40:29.771 --> 00:40:30.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:40:37.049 --> 00:40:38.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to have this.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:40:38.208 --> 00:40:42.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's an original Kira Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It could be very valuable one day.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:40:43.086 --> 00:40:44.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear she didn't make many.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:40:44.926 --> 00:40:46.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:40:49.004 --> 00:40:51.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought your speech</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>went very well yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:40:51.525 --> 00:40:52.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was the right thing to do.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:40:53.344 --> 00:40:55.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted everyone to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what happened to Akorem</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:40:56.202 --> 00:40:58.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that the Prophets said nothing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about returning to the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

654
00:41:00.677 --> 00:41:02.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just about everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was relieved to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:41:02.477 --> 00:41:04.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's your own fault.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can't believe you didn't cover me.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:41:04.680 --> 00:41:06.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was I to know you were going to insult</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the King of Leinster?</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:41:06.700 --> 00:41:08.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ah!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-In his own keep!</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:41:08.140 --> 00:41:09.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:41:10.158 --> 00:41:13.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just reading one of Akorem's poems,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Call of the Prophets.</i></c.bg_transparent>

660
00:41:13.837 --> 00:41:15.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that's one of my favorites.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:15.300 --> 00:41:16.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a shame he never finished it.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:41:17.299 --> 00:41:18.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He did. Look.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:41:22.537 --> 00:41:23.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is confusing.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:41:25.395 --> 00:41:29.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last time I read this poem,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it ended after the 12th stanza.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:41:30.304 --> 00:41:31.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the timeline's been changed,</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:41:32.417 --> 00:41:34.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then why do I remember things</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way they used to be?</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:41:35.251 --> 00:41:37.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets work in mysterious ways.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:41:40.210 --> 00:41:41.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: Excuse me, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:41:41.529 --> 00:41:42.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:41:42.949 --> 00:41:46.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry to bother you, but tomorrow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after evening services in the Temple,</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:41:46.691 --> 00:41:48.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we're having my daughter's</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>ih'tanu </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>ceremony.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:41:51.087 --> 00:41:52.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's turning 14.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:41:53.126 --> 00:41:53.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Happy birthday.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:41:55.625 --> 00:41:59.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were wondering if there's any chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you could come and give her your blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:42:00.024 --> 00:42:01.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would mean so much to us.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:42:02.102 --> 00:42:03.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd be happy to.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:42:04.863 --> 00:42:05.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:42:07.022 --> 00:42:07.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're welcome.</c.bg_transparent>

